{"tid":1545960,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"2.5B只買大波心水channel","createTime":"2019-09-06T06:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T12:55:57.000Z","uid":263506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf7c43322fdb487615a0fd89f18b73e4a108d132","tid":1545960,"uid":263506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"「自從淨係買大波之後，我賭波人生唔同矖🔥🔥」<br />\n<br />\n自從淨係買大波之後，我唔使再驚對家入波，唔使再驚買左嗰隊比人456，唔使再嗌反cup，唔使再怕贏波輸盤。<br />\n<br />\n自從淨係買大波之後，每一場波就好似兩隊一齊幫我賺錢咁，邊隊入波我都開心。唔會再因為對家秒入而心up，而係會因為有人入波而高興。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買大波幫我追返晒所有輸落嘅錢，而我希望可以以係尼個channel出嘅水幫各位手足追數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你信我嘅就click join，我哋一齊屠馬會🔥🔥🔥<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/data25b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdata25b&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=d42c78f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/data25b</a><br />\n<br />\n[賭無必勝，我嘅心水亦不是100%，請自行分配注碼]"},{"pid":"f064267315d2b0412076ae30d72e962a97a27f54","tid":1545960,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:00:24.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9aec8db72a1483d8160e985d033a64b1ae671a78","tid":1545960,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:00:32.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n